DONNA EDWARDS, APPLICANT, v. MAYOR AND COUNCIL OF THE BOROUGH OF MOONACHIE, RESPONDENT. Argued January 21, 1948 Decided March 29, 1948.

Before Case, Chiee Justice, and Justice Bueling.

For the applicant, Leo Rosenblum and Sebastian Gaeta. For the respondent, Chandless, Weller, Kramer & Frank (Ralph W. Chandless). Per Curiam.

The application presents debatable questions of law. A writ may be presented for 'allocatur.
